Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_rx::_stats_pkts_drp

Count of all packets received that were dropped due to a full receive FIFO. This counts good and bad packets received - all packets dropped by the FIFO. It does not count packets dropped by the dmac or pause packet filters.
